| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5063 — Recovery Inhibition (blackshrantac)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e5f66f5c-028f-5e74-a168-fa5b6766c77c"
